metadata.name: Invisible Enemies Official: Mint Pass
metadata.description: Mint Passes for Invisible Enemies NFT project. Invisible Enemies is an awareness driven NFT project set to drop on January 22. The community seeks to build a brand in and out of the NFT space that everyone recognizes and knows. Raising awareness on mental health issues facing our veterans and creating a space where supporters and veterans can come together to have fun, share stories, get support and resources as well as learning to make money. Our investors get as much value back to them as possible through any utilities they ultimately decide using the platform and foundation we set to create. 10% of profit revenue goes to charity.
